latestPosts.caption:
I Met My Subscribers in Lucknow 💖 
@ramsha.sultan.khan 

This was one of the most emotional and unforgettable moments of my journey as a YouTuber in India — my first visit to Lucknow and an unplanned meet and greet that turned into something magical! 🌸✨

At 2 AM, I randomly posted that if anyone from Lucknow wanted to meet me, they could come to Moiza Studio in Ameenabad Market the next day — and I was not expecting what happened next. The response was overwhelming! 💫

The entire shop was packed — literally no space to even stand. People of all age groups came — young girls, families, mothers with kids, even elderly uncles and aunties. Many of you brought your parents, made me speak to your relatives on phone, clicked selfies, gifted handmade cards, and some of you even had tears in your eyes saying it felt like a dream come true. 🥺

Some beautiful souls opened up about their personal struggles, asked for advice, and showed me a kind of love that I will never forget. This meet and greet was more than just a gathering — it was a reminder of the beautiful connection we share through faith, sisterhood, and support. 💕

JazakAllah Khair to everyone who came and made this moment so special.

📍 Location: Ameenabad Market, Lucknow
🕌 Occasion: Surprise Meet & Greet at Moiza Studio

✨ A more detailed vlog of my Lucknow visit is coming soon, InshaAllah.

⭐️ For collaborations, email at ramshasultanwork@gmail.com
